Laurie will be flying the flag high for the beauty brand in South Africa, Brazil and the States.The exciting announcement was made at a celebratory party at Beechwood Gardens, Hyde Park, South Africa, on November 29 2016.Brand manager of Vichy South Africa, Florentine Ammer, said that Laurie s passion for skincare makes her a perfect fit for the brand. As ambassador for Vichy South Africa, we believe that Liesl embodies the values of the brand wholeheartedly, and understands the importance of health as a means to beauty, said Ammer.The beauty pageant winner is excited to be associated with the international brand."One of the biggest blessings of 2016 is being a part of a family that values my input, respects my views and has set out to make every woman feel comfortable in their own skin, she said.She added that this opportunity will help her to grow from strength to strength. The opportunity of being the ambassador for such an extraordinary brand has created a whirlwind of excitement for [me] and my family."Check out the photos of the Vichy event that Laurie shared on Instagram:A photo posted by Liesl Laurie (@liesllaurie) on Nov 29, 2016 at 7:38am PSTA photo posted by Liesl Laurie (@liesllaurie) on Nov 29, 2016 at 5:56am PSTA photo posted by Liesl Laurie (@liesllaurie) on Nov 29, 2016 at 7:51am PST Find the hottest celebrity and entertainment news on TshisaLIVE or follow TshisaLIVE on Facebook and Twitter. 